Shawna Waldron https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shawna_Waldron 0 Shawna Langill Waldron (born January 25, 1982) is an American actress. Waldron is best known for her roles as Becky O'Shea in the 1994 sports comedy film Little Giants and as Bonnie Stiles on CBS television series Ladies Man.
